{
  "component": "GradientView",
  "kebab": "gradient-view",
  "aliasOf": null,
  "title": "GradientView",
  "description": {
    "en": "View with a linear gradient background. For simple 2-stop gradients, the `gradient` attribute on a regular View is sufficient — use GradientView when `locations` (multi-stop control) is needed.",
    "ja": "線形グラデーション背景を持つ View。2 色の単純なグラデーションなら通常の View の `gradient` 属性で十分、`locations`（多段 stop 制御）が必要なときに GradientView を使う。"
  },
  "usage": {
    "en": "Use GradientView for hero banners, card overlays, and any background needing 3+ color stops or precise stop positions. For flat colors, prefer `background` on a View.",
    "ja": "ヒーローバナー、カードオーバーレイ、3 色以上の stop や精密な位置指定が必要な背景に使う。単色背景は View の `background` を使う。"
  },
  "aliasNotice": null,
